      • inPrettyBraces

        public static java.lang.String inPrettyBraces(java.lang.String original,
                                              java.lang.String margin,
                                              java.lang.String indent)
        Returns original string wrapped with new lines and braces, and appropriate margin. Returned value is composed as: <space>{ <margin><indent><original> <margin>}
        Parameters:
        original - Original string to modify
        margin - String representing the current margin to indent.
        indent - String representing how much to indent original in addition to margin.
        Returns:
        Original string wrapped in new lines, then braces, and appropriate indents.
